  "body": "## Bug Report\r\n**What did you do?**\r\n\r\nStart prometheus with aggressive settings (--storage.tsdb.max-block-duration=10m --storage.tsdb.min-block-duration=1m)\r\n\r\nWait for a checkpoint:\r\ndata/wal/checkpoint.000040/\r\n\r\nLet's say that the checkpoint has a size of 5M\r\n\r\nCopy the checkpoint to data/wal/checkpoint.000042.tmp\r\n\r\n_It simulates the case where the tmp checkpoint is not written completely_\r\n\r\n\r\n**What did you expect to see?**\r\n\r\nwhen checkpoint 0000042 is written, its size is 5M\r\n\r\n**What did you see instead? Under which circumstances?**\r\n\r\n\r\ncheckpoint 0000042 is 10M, because it contains the tmp that was not written successfully.\r\n\r\n**Environment**\r\n\r\nLinux\r\n\r\n\r\n* Prometheus version:\r\n\r\n2.15.2\r\n",
